PrecisApproval (a) to enter into an AGREEMENT with COMMERCIAL PHEASANT PRODUCERS COOPERATIVE LTD. which provides for the implementation of a cooperative plan for the marketing of GRADE "A" PHEASANT produced in Saskatchewan during 1991, and (b) for the appointment of T.D.
